comments: Quickley (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Quickley (TOR) is already in Henderson's (POR) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Olynyk (TOR) keeps his foot planted to the floor and does not intentionally kick the ball on the play.
After the ball is deflected by Olynyk (TOR), Thybulle (POR) legally gains possession in the backcourt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) cleanly deflects the ball away from Thybulle (POR) during his drive.
Trent Jr. (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Thybulle (POR).
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Olynyk (TOR) moves somewhat laterally towards Camara (POR), and the contact in the backcourt is marginal.
Replay review of the foul called on Dick (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Dick moves laterally into Simons' (POR) path and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Camara (POR) slides his hand across Quickley's (TOR) upper body, and the contact during the drive is marginal.
Thybulle (POR) iextends his forearm into Boucher (TOR) and delivers contact that dislodges him from his legally obtained rebounding position.
Olynyk (TOR) is already in Camara's (POR) path and does not deliver contact.
Boucher (TOR) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.

Replay review of the foul called on Camara (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Camara extends his lower body forward and initiates contact with Boucher (TOR) that affects his shot near the rim.
Boucher (TOR) is moving alongside Simons' (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together in the backcourt.
A jump ball is called to determine possession.  Simons (POR) is the last player to touch the ball, and possession should have been awarded to the Raptors.
Olynyk (TOR) establishes himself in Murray's (POR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Murray (POR) brings his arm forward towards Olynyk's (TOR) front, and marginal contact occurs as they briefly engage on the perimeter.
Olynyk (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Thybulle (POR) as they pursue the rebound.
Boucher's (TOR) momentum carries him backwards into Murray (POR), and the contact after the shot near the rim is marginal.
Olynyk (TOR) grasps and then quickly releases Ayton's (POR) jersey while the pass is in the air.
Ayton (POR) brings his hands towards Olynyk's (TOR) front and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to receive the pass.
Olynyk (TOR) raises his hand into a vertical position and legally contests Ayton's (POR) shot near the rim.
